{"tid":656420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"強風吹倒看板砸傷　26歲女偶像半身不遂","createTime":"2018-05-07T08:57:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-07T17:55:47.000Z","uid":130626,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"95813ff11aba48cd43d8cb7c0e5820ba24e57efe","tid":656420,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T08:57:37.000Z","msg":"日本地下偶像女團「假面女子」26歲成員豬狩友香，4月11日下午在東京路上，被強風吹倒的看板擊中腰部骨折重傷，被路人報警送加護病房治療，今透露因脊椎損傷導致下肢麻痺，今後都必須坐輪椅生活，讓人相當不捨。<br />\n <br />\n她目前仍住院復健，練習使用輪椅生活，預計還要3個月才能出院。其經紀公司表示，她出院後仍會以「假面女子」成員身分活動。（吳惠菁／綜合報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180507/640_ba8d1b6a311e9c3c9438069e7e910da1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180507%2F640_ba8d1b6a311e9c3c9438069e7e910da1.jpg&h=bde374d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20180507/1348999\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20180507%2F1348999&d=4tRPLw2x%2Bopihp7tnb4LpW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=7cf59311\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20180507%2F1348999&h=07b6f028\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20180507/1348999</a>"},{"pid":"0fa049d942183b54bd0ba583da79772705ebe89b","tid":656420,"uid":121130,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T09:00:21.000Z","msg":"佢仲笑得落好野"},{"pid":"02b7e159c0babab588f9ae529749b78206261649","tid":656420,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T16:30:22.000Z","msg":"推post"},{"pid":"3c1c9a0272f7d76818c511ad0afdd882c671dc91","tid":656420,"uid":91982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T17:12:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e6edaab77873eaa305761066ae425755d99ff73c","tid":656420,"uid":99205,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"201